<br />
<span style="color: #000000;">Plus, the license update plan includes </span><b><span style="color: #ff6600;">1 FREE support month & 3 FREE update months</span><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></b><span style="color: #000000;">to future releases. </span><br />
                            Thus, within 3 months from your license update purchase date, if there might be                            a new release , you are entitled to update free of charge.<br />
